  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Close your eyes and imagine the perfect golf course. Whether you conjure up an image of a real-life, world famous course or visualize a championship course all of your own design - if you can dream it, you can play it with Greg Norman's GOLF POWER. Our exclusive course designer with battery back-up allows you to customize your own 18-hole championship course and then save it in memory. Create a dream course, play one of the pre-set courses in England, Scotland, the USA or Japan, or rejoin a saved game right where you left off. Just like the Great White Shark, you'll need total concentration, strategy and control to make the leader board.",
